      <title>银行家称 2024 年并购交易“本应很棒”，但现在却很顺利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/bankers-say-2024-m-a-is-just-good-when-it-should-ve-been-great</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年年初出现的一系列大型交易未能转化为并购活动的持续复苏，因为这一势头受到央行担忧和地缘政治不安的阻碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/bankers-say-2024-m-a-is-just-good-when-it-should-ve-been-great</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
