      <title>印度信贷受益于指数相关债券流动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/india-credit-seen-benefiting-from-index-related-bond-flows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度 2 万亿美元固定收益市场中少数几位女性管理者之一表示，随着印度加入全球债券指数，流入印度的资本将逐渐流入公司债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/india-credit-seen-benefiting-from-index-related-bond-flows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
